#: ../../hardware/controllers/roland_dj_505.md:17
msgid ""
"The Roland DJ-505 is an all-in-one USB {term}`MIDI` controller with an "
"integrated audio interface. It has controls for 2 decks that can be toggled "
"between decks to play with 4 decks. It also features a TR-S step sequencer "
"with sounds from the TR-808 and the TR-909 drum machines (TR-606 and TR-707 "
"are available via firmware update)."
msgstr ""

