#: ../../hardware/controllers/roland_dj_505.md:62
msgid ""
"The knobs for {hwlabel}`MASTER LEVEL`, {hwlabel}`BOOTH LEVEL`, "
"{hwlabel}`PHONES VOLUME`, {hwlabel}`MIC LEVEL`, {hwlabel}`TR/SAMPLER LEVEL` "
"and {hwlabel}`CUE/MASTER MIXING` are controlling the hardware mixer of the "
"built-in audio interface. Hence, turning the knobs will not change values in"
" the Mixxx {term}`GUI` and you’ll need to set the Mixxx knobs to their "
"default values when using the controller:"
msgstr ""

